title: Queens of the Stoneage - Songs For The Deaf DVD
description:
This is the video DVD which was included with the initial release of QOTSA\\\&#039;s Songs For The Deaf in 2002. Track listing is as follows:

Monster In The Parasol
No One Knows
The Lost Art of Keeping A Secret
Quick & To The Pointless
Queens of the Fucking Stoneage
+Interview

This is all live stuff and features Dave Grohl on drums on most songs. This is my first attempt at doing this so feedback is appreciated!
